# Group Invoice
## List Invoices [/api/v1/invoices{?per_page,include}]
### List Invoices [GET]

View a listing of all invoices.

+ Admin to retrieve all invoices, or patient to retrieve only own invoices.

+ Parameters
    + per_page: `2` (number, optional) - Enables pagination and set items per page.
    + include: `invoice_items` (string, optional) - Join relationship data.
        + Members
            + `invoice_items`
            + `patient.user`
            + `patient`
+ Request
    + Headers
        Authorization: Bearer {{ ACCESS_TOKEN }}
        X-Requested-With: XMLHttpRequest
        Content-Type: application/json
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Headers
    + Body
