## Get Invoice Items [/api/v1/invoices/{invoice_id}/invoice_items{?include}]
### Get Invoice Items [GET]

Get a invoice items by Invoice ID.

+ Require Admin or current logged in User as the Patient of the Invoice.

+ Parameters
    + invoice_id: `1` (number, required) - Must be a valid ID.
    + include: `invoice_items` (string, optional) - Join relationship data.
        + Members
            + `invoice_items`
            + `patient,user`
            + `patient`
